description:
What will it take to get in a position where our loving Savior is able to protect us from the false Christs, false prophets, and false wonders that are to come upon the earth just before Jesus returns? We're told these deceptions will be so powerful, even the elect will be deceived, if that were possible. Have you ever wondered what it takes to be at peace? How do we cooperate with the Lord as He protects us from the overpowering deceptions taking the world captive? These are the questions Dan Gabbert helps answer in this eye-opening presentation.

Visit our website: http://amazingdiscoveries.org

http://amazingdiscoveries.tv/media/892/802g-klto-plan/
